      "role": "user",
      "content": "got it. what about cases where the loss is caused by something unpredictable like severe weather or maybe even theft/piracy? does the CIF insurance usually cover those kinds of \"unforeseen\" maritime incidents, or are we still on the hook if things go south out in the middle of the ocean?",
